Popular Instagram comedian, Aloma Issac Junior aka Zicsaloma has gifted himself with a Mercedes Benz SUV. The online sensation, who quit lecturing for comedy, is known for his dramatic yet iconic female character displays leaving fans laughing hysterically. Taking to Instagram to share the news, Zicsaloma reposted a video of his new car on his Insta story after his fellow comic actor, Nons Miraj had shared the news on her page. The video also shows that Zicsaloma and his colleague have already named his new car, a 2015 Mercedes Benz ML as they could be heard excitedly saying; “Nono baby has landed.” The Kaduna-born comic act was also a contestant at ‘The Voice Nigeria’ and ‘Nigerian Idol’.